description:
A bottle of aged fashioned bay rum following shave! Get that great just out of the barber's chair scent and really feel when you splash some of this on your cheeks following a awesome shave. description:

Comes in a huge 8 oz. tub!

Apply after using our fine Suavecito Pomade Shaving Crème.
